n. Semangat! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wallahu a‚Äôlam bisshawab.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mau Dibawa Kemana Ramadhan Kali Ini?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1411-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-05-03 00:49:57', '2020-05-02 17:49:57', '', 1411, 'http://ukijashtis.or.id/2020/05/03/1411-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
